description.en: BABYELON is an open source peer-to-peer digital currency on the ethereum blockchain that distinguishes itself from other digital currencies in the crypto space through its aim in cultivating a vibrant, productive, and supportive community. Relatedly, as a community driven project, BabyElon rewards holders with an innovative reflection rate, as 5% of transactions is redistributed among existing holders. It is these elements, jointly combined with an experienced team of developers and influencers in the cryptocurrency space that set up BABYELON for long-term growth and progress.
